        "content": "<p>Just in time for the New Year, <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"398581\">@Mantas Baksys</span> and I unsorried our proof of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kneser%27s_theorem_(combinatorics)\">Kneser's addition theorem</a>. This is an additive combinatorics generalisation of the classical <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Restricted_sumset#Cauchy%E2%80%93Davenport_theorem\">Cauchy-Davenport theorem</a>.</p>",
